Is e a tha ann an '''drochaid''', Sructur a bhreitheas rathad, frith-rathad, neo slighe eile thar beàrn. Mar is tric bithidh am bearn seo eadar da bhruaich aibhne.


Is iad na tri priomh cruthan drochaide

1. Drochaid Saile

2. Drochaid Bhogha

3. Drochaid nam Ball ( no drochaid croichte)


== Drochaid Saile ==


Chan ann an cruth as simplidh de '''drochaid saile ''' ach leac (cloiche) neo maide (fiodh) sinte thar allt. Nuair a rachas eallach air drochaid sailtheachd, theid cromadh air na sailibh.

